data.description: Discover two charming homes nestled on 14 acres of serene privacy, just 15-20 minutes from Orofino. This remarkable property boasts fruit trees, abundant wildlife, stunning views, and easy access to some of the finest fishing and hunting opportunities in the area. The main house, with 1326 sq ft, offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an updated kitchen with new stainless steel appliances, a covered deck, a screened-in patio, and a spacious living room complete with a wood stove and electric wall heat. Additionally, a sizable barn with a loft provides ample storage for all your equipment and toys. The second home, a beautifully renovated 792 sq ft gem, features 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, a gorgeous kitchen, and exquisite interior details. Currently, the second home rents for $950 per month, making it a lucrative investment option.  Both homes share one parcel, with an additional 3-acre parcel included. There may also be possibility to divide the property.
